<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>404 Error - Page Not Found</title>
    <style>
        * {
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            box-sizing: border-box;
            font-family: 'Arial', sans-serif;
        }

        body {
            display: flex;
            justify-content: center;
            align-items: center;
            height: 100vh;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #1e3c72, #2a5298);
            color: white;
            text-align: center;
        }

        .error-container {
            max-width: 600px;
            padding: 20px;
            background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1);
            backdrop-filter: blur(10px);
            border-radius: 15px;
            box-shadow: 0px 0px 15px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.2);
            animation: fadeIn 1.2s ease-in-out;
        }

        h1 {
            font-size: 100px;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
            color: #ffcc00;
            text-shadow: 3px 3px 5px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.3);
        }

        h2 {
            font-size: 24px;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }

        p {
            font-size: 18px;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
            opacity: 0.8;
        }

        .btn {
            padding: 10px 20px;
            font-size: 18px;
            color: white;
            background: #ff5733;
            border: none;
            border-radius: 8px;
            cursor: pointer;
            transition: 0.3s;
            text-decoration: none;
        }

        .btn:hover {
            background: #ff784f;
        }

        @keyframes fadeIn {
            from {
                opacity: 0;
                transform: translateY(-20px);
            }
            to {
                opacity: 1;
                transform: translateY(0);
            }
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="error-container">
        <h1>404</h1>
        <h2>Oops! Page Not Found</h2>
        <p>The page you're looking for doesn't exist or an error occurred.</p>
        <a href="/Home" class="btn">Go Back Home</a>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
